From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: darealshinji <djcj@gmx.de>
Date: Sun, 24 Jul 2016 09:33:22 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] define XXX_EXPORT symbols


